    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Re-learn how to use your hands from scratch in <i>Chef Hands : Kitch</i>en Mayhem !</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179160/extras/e915097e43d2fb4f24717674e8f4d146.avif?t=1766055941\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179160/extras_big/e915097e43d2fb4f24717674e8f4d146.webp?t=1766055941 width=1560 height=390 /></span><br><strong>The Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you directly control a hand with basic but hard to master controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179160/extras/a3d991bfecad8a5bcd293d45bab84456.poster.avif?t=1766055941\" width=838 height=678 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179160/extras/a3d991bfecad8a5bcd293d45bab84456.webm?t=1766055941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179160/extras/a3d991bfecad8a5bcd293d45bab84456.mp4?t=1766055941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To show off your dexterity, you’ll be put in various kitchens and will be tasked with preparing food in a timely manner for our customers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The kitchens</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179160/extras/05e82bdfdd588c8c2a50fa94df01d228.avif?t=1766055941\" width=1024 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Burger Kitchen</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook burgers and steaks in a restaurant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moving Food Truck</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make breakfast while in a moving food truck on the road. Ingredients jump with the bumps !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cruise ship</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to make sandwiches on a ship rocking with the waves. Everything is sliding around !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space station</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try the challenging low gravity environment that the space station offers while enjoying a nice view of our planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speeding Food Truck</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now prove your skills by making burgers while speeding down a badly shaped road. Ingredients that you don’t keep an eye on will fly off the door.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can upgrade your kitchens with the money you earn. This will make you more efficient and will allow you to earn more. For example, you can improve the cooking speed of the stove or forget about washing the plates.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Local fun</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Too much for one chef ? Split the tasks among a maximum of 4 chefs locally !</p>",
